Mobile SDK Mapping

To create a 360-degree view of a Mobile App user based on Data Cloud Mobile SDK data and MobilePush (in Marketing Cloud Engagement) bundles, use the model diagram and mapping recommendations.

To match on Party ID, map the Identification Number, Party Identification Type, and Identification Name. To map these fields, see Use Case 7: Create Required Party Identifier Formula Fields for Mobile.
